This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for paraphrase identification, which are common topics in the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves attention mechanisms and pretraining, which are relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and neural networks (cs.NE).
